    "His biography began a series of scholarly English-language-authored biographies on the artist by <a href=\"/rewaldj\">John Rewald</a>, <a href=\"/lindsayj\">Jack Lindsay</a> and <a href=\"/nochlinl\">Linda Nochlin</a>.": [],
